OL,3,CVolunteer 'blood bike rider' dies on
OL,4,CNew Year's Day after crash
OL,6,FA volunteer motorcyclist transporting
OL,7,Fmedical supplies has died following a
OL,8,Fcrash in Carmarthenshire.
OL,10,FAndrew Rogers, 61, was volunteering as
OL,11,Fa "blood bike rider" - a volunteer
OL,12,Fmotorcyclist who transports urgent
OL,13,Fmedical supplies - at the time of the
OL,14,Fcrash on Monday, 29 December.
