OL,3,CVolunteer 'blood bike rider' dies on
OL,4,CNew Year's Day after crash
OL,6,FHe was admitted to hospital in a
OL,7,Fcritical condition following the crash
OL,8,Finvolving a Honda 750 Liveried Blood
OL,9,FBike and a black Audi A3 on the A48,
OL,10,Fwestbound between the Botanical
OL,11,FGardens turning and Llanddarog
OL,12,Fjunction.
OL,14,FDyfed-Powys Police has now confirmed
OL,15,Fhe died on Thursday, 1 January.
