OL,6,FPaying tribute to the husband, father,
OL,7,Fson, brother, grandfather and uncle,
OL,8,Fhis family said in a statement:
OL,9,F"Andrew was volunteering as blood bike
OL,10,Frider at the time, something he was
OL,11,Fdeeply passionate about.
OL,13,F"Helping people and volunteering as
OL,14,Fstreet pastor for many years, Andrew
OL,15,Fhad a strong Christian faith, with his
OL,16,Flife guided by his Lord Jesus.
