OL,6,F"Andrew was a farmer his whole life
OL,7,Fand it was his passion. He was well-
OL,8,Fknown, loved, and respected within the
OL,9,Ffarming community and extremely
OL,10,Fknowledgeable: knowledge he passed
OL,11,Fdown to his children and grandchildren
OL,12,Fover the years.
OL,14,F"Andrew will be remembered by his wife
OL,15,FTricia, daughter Julie, son and his
OL,16,Fpartner Nathan and Penny, mum Hilda,
OL,17,Fbrother and sister-in-law Colin and
OL,18,FMyra, grandchildren Cerys, Iwan, and
OL,19,FMyfanwy, nieces and nephews Megan,
OL,20,FKiki, and Dominic, and the wider
OL,21,Ffamily and friends."
