OL,6,FPolice said on Tuesday that the driver
OL,7,Fof the Audi ` a 26-year-old man ` was
OL,8,Farrested on suspicion of causing
OL,9,Fserious injury by careless driving.
OL,11,FOfficers are continuing to appeal for
OL,12,Fanyone who was travelling westbound on
OL,13,Fthe A48 near Llanddarog just before
OL,14,F6pm on Monday 29 December to contact
OL,15,Fthem.
